Package org.lukep.javavis.visualisation

Class Summary
Visualisation Represents a visualisation in the system and is asssociated both an IVisualiser class and an IVisualiserVisitor.
VisualisationRegistry The VisualisationRegistry is a singleton that stores all of the Visualisations in the program's memory.
